二 、LNMP+Redis
	2.1 部署lnmp环境
  283  yum -y install gcc pcre-devel zlib-devel
  284  tar -zxvf nginx-1.12.2.tar.gz 
   286  cd nginx-1.12.2/
  287  ./configure 
  288  make
  289  make install
  291  ls /usr/local/nginx/
